# VHS Tape: Progress Bar Widget - Multiline Progress Bars
# Shows rich, color, and plain modes rendering simultaneously with new init_progress_bars API

Output demos/progress.gif

# Terminal settings
Set Width 800
Set Height 400
Set FontSize 14
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set CursorBlink false

# Execute the demo
Type "./demo_progress.sh"
Enter

# Wait for animation to complete
Sleep 4s

# Final pause to view all three completed bars
Sleep 2s
